LoginTC,provides,a,two,factor,authentication,system,that,can,be,used,with,networks,websites,and,both,mobile,and,online,applications,The,system,uses,LoginTC,credentials,on,smartphones,in,combination,with,a,traditional,username,and,password,for,authentication,This,means,that,a,potential,hacker,would,have,to,possess,both,a,user,s,password,and,their,smartphone,in,order,to,breach,an,account,The,LoginTC,REST,API,allows,users,to,perform,common,administrative,tasks,and,to,send,and,check,authentication,sessions,with,end,users